                    <span>Those of us in the publishing business could not get through a week without the book. Congratulations to the Chicago Manual of Style on its 15th edition.<P>Eric Bollinger<BR>McKenna Publishing Group<BR>Publisher of "Two Dozen Lessons From An Editor" by Jim Woods.</span>
                  
              
